header.gameNote: AARON'S AMERICAN ATHLETIC CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Conner Frankamp draws the foul and hits a midrange jump shot for a chance at 3-point play.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Frankamp connects on and-1 jumper

videos.description: Wichita State's Landry Shamet throws a one-handed touch pass to Rashard Kelly for a slam.
videos.headline: Kelly runs the floor for two-handed flush

videos.description: Wichita State's Landry Shamet drains five 3-pointers, including a deep 3-pointer before the halftime buzzer.
videos.headline: Shamet hits nothing but net before buzzer

videos.description: Shaquille Morris is accessed a flagrant foul after he appears to intentionally tries to trip Josh Brown during a fast break.
videos.headline: Morris called for flagrant after apparent trip

videos.description: Quinton Rose comes from behind to force the turnover and races up the court for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Temple's Rose gets breakaway dunk

videos.description: Austin Reaves delivers a lob to Markis McDuffie after a steal for a  bench-pleasing slam.
videos.headline: Wichita State's bench erupts after McDuffie dunk

videos.description: J.P. Moorman II splits two Wichita State defenders and flips in a basket while getting fouled and earns a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Temple's Moorman gets tough and-1 bucket
